data.description: Welcome to the country home of your dreams! This fantastic property boasts 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, a finished walk-out basement, finished attic space, and a beautiful wrap around porch. With just under 4,000 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room to spread out and host your family comfortably for the holidays this year! Nestled on the property is a large horse barn complete with an indoor arena and heated/cooled tack room. With over 12 acres this property ensures your horses also have plenty of room to roam and graze while away from the barn. This home features a 3 car detached garage offering plenty of space for your vehicles, tractors, toys, and more!  This property offers the best of both worlds - country living with the convenience of being approximately 15 minutes from downtown Columbus and Greensburg. Don't miss out on this opportunity to snag this one of a kind property before it's gone!
